data.description:
Amazing townhouse in a great area, located near the I-15 freeway and easy access to Logan. The townhouse has 5 bedrooms/3 bathrooms, 2900 square feet, and is available now! You'll enjoy a spacious 2 car garage, stainless steel appliances, granite counter tops, a spacious master bedroom, walk-in closet, and right off the Eagle Mountain Golf Course. No smoking/vaping in or on the property. Pets under 40 lbs are allowed with a pet fee and deposit Tenants: - Application fee $37 per applicant 18 or older
- Responsible only to signup/pay gas utility - Lease setup fee $50
- Renters insurance provided for $16/month If interested contact Emil at to view and apply for this property.
